version: 0.0.1 (name: noob)

Description: A simple extension to reverse your url. Many sites put links to download in reverse way, forcing the navigator to fill a register enterily . With this extension you can put the url normal way again, no more register unnecessary.

Usage: Just click on the file Reverse URL.oex or drag it on Opera.

